section#about.page-section.about-page
    .container
        section.about-who-we-are
            .about-section-intro
                p.about-section-label(data-i18n='about.profile.kicker', data-en='Who We Are' data-zh='公司简介') Who We Are
                h2.about-section-title
                    span.about-title-zh 面向工业应用的
                        br
                        | 专业密封件供应商
                    span.about-title-en(data-i18n='about.profile.titleEn', data-en='A Professional Industrial Sealing Supplier with Practical Application Expertise' data-zh='A Professional Industrial Sealing Supplier with Practical Application Expertise') A Professional Industrial Sealing Supplier with Practical Application Expertise
            .about-section-copy
                p(data-i18n='about.profile.copy1', data-en='We are a professional supplier of industrial sealing products, offering a wide range of standard and engineered seals for global applications.' data-zh='我们是一家专业从事工业密封件供应的企业，提供涵盖标准件与工程密封件的完整产品体系，服务全球多行业客户。') We are a professional supplier of industrial sealing products, offering a wide range of standard and engineered seals for global applications.
                p(data-i18n='about.profile.copy2', data-en='Backed by years of industry experience and a fully integrated supply chain, we provide not only products, but also practical sealing solutions tailored to real working conditions.' data-zh='依托多年的行业经验与完善的供应链体系，我们不仅提供产品，更根据实际工况提供切实可行的密封解决方案。') Backed by years of industry experience and a fully integrated supply chain, we provide not only products, but also practical sealing solutions tailored to real working conditions.

        section.about-numbers
            .about-section-heading
                p.about-section-label(data-i18n='about.metrics.kicker', data-en='Our Strength in Numbers' data-zh='实力数据') Our Strength in Numbers
                h2.about-section-title
                    span.about-title-zh(data-i18n='about.metrics.titleZh', data-en='By the Numbers' data-zh='用数据说明实力') By the Numbers
                    span.about-title-en(data-i18n='about.metrics.titleEn', data-en='Trusted by Experience, Proven by Numbers' data-zh='Trusted by Experience, Proven by Numbers') Trusted by Experience, Proven by Numbers
            .about-numbers-grid
                article.about-number-card
                    strong(data-i18n='about.metrics.item1.value', data-en='20+' data-zh='20+') 20+
                    span(data-i18n='about.metrics.item1.label', data-en='Years of Industry Experience' data-zh='年行业经验') Years of Industry Experience
                article.about-number-card
                    strong(data-i18n='about.metrics.item2.value', data-en='3000+' data-zh='3000+') 3000+
                    span(data-i18n='about.metrics.item2.label', data-en='Product Types' data-zh='产品种类') Product Types
                article.about-number-card
                    strong(data-i18n='about.metrics.item3.value', data-en='10+' data-zh='10+') 10+
                    span(data-i18n='about.metrics.item3.label', data-en='Industries Served' data-zh='服务行业') Industries Served
                article.about-number-card
                    strong(data-i18n='about.metrics.item4.value', data-en='5 Key Stages' data-zh='5大环节') 5 Key Stages
                    span(data-i18n='about.metrics.item4.label', data-en='Raw Materials to Technical Support' data-zh='原材料到技术支持') Raw Materials to Technical Support
                article.about-number-card
                    strong(data-i18n='about.metrics.item5.value', data-en='Global' data-zh='全球') Global
                    span(data-i18n='about.metrics.item5.label', data-en='Supply Capability' data-zh='供货能力') Supply Capability

        section.about-strengths
            .about-section-heading
                p.about-section-label(data-i18n='about.strengths.kicker', data-en='Our Strength' data-zh='核心优势') Our Strength
                h2.about-section-title
                    span.about-title-zh(data-i18n='about.strengths.titleZh', data-en='Our Strength' data-zh='把真正的竞争力说清楚') Our Strength
                    span.about-title-en(data-i18n='about.strengths.titleEn', data-en='What Makes CHX a Reliable Sealing Supply Partner' data-zh='What Makes CHX a Reliable Sealing Supply Partner') What Makes CHX a Reliable Sealing Supply Partner
            .about-strengths-grid
                article.about-strength-card
                    .about-strength-icon
                        i.fa-solid.fa-link(aria-hidden='true')
                    h3(data-i18n='about.strengths.item1.title', data-en='Integrated Supply Chain' data-zh='供应链一体化') Integrated Supply Chain
                    p(data-i18n='about.strengths.item1.text', data-en='From raw materials to manufacturing, logistics, storage, and technical support, we ensure seamless coordination and consistent quality control.' data-zh='覆盖原材料采购、生产制造、仓储物流及技术支持，实现全流程高效协同与质量可控。') From raw materials to manufacturing, logistics, storage, and technical support, we ensure seamless coordination and consistent quality control.
                article.about-strength-card
                    .about-strength-icon
                        i.fa-solid.fa-shield-halved(aria-hidden='true')
                    h3(data-i18n='about.strengths.item2.title', data-en='Quality Assurance System' data-zh='品质保障体系') Quality Assurance System
                    p(data-i18n='about.strengths.item2.text', data-en='Each stage is supported by a strict quality management system, ensuring stable performance and long-term reliability.' data-zh='各环节均建立严格的质量管理体系，确保产品性能稳定可靠，满足工业级应用需求。') Each stage is supported by a strict quality management system, ensuring stable performance and long-term reliability.
                article.about-strength-card
                    .about-strength-icon
                        i.fa-solid.fa-layer-group(aria-hidden='true')
                    h3(data-i18n='about.strengths.item3.title', data-en='Extensive Product Range' data-zh='丰富产品体系') Extensive Product Range
                    p(data-i18n='about.strengths.item3.text', data-en='We offer a comprehensive portfolio covering hydraulic seals, pneumatic seals, oil seals, and engineered sealing solutions.' data-zh='涵盖液压密封、气动密封、油封及工程密封件，满足多种工况与行业需求。') We offer a comprehensive portfolio covering hydraulic seals, pneumatic seals, oil seals, and engineered sealing solutions.
                article.about-strength-card
                    .about-strength-icon
                        i.fa-solid.fa-compass-drafting(aria-hidden='true')
                    h3(data-i18n='about.strengths.item4.title', data-en='Solution-Oriented Approach' data-zh='解决方案导向') Solution-Oriented Approach
                    p(data-i18n='about.strengths.item4.text', data-en='We go beyond products to deliver practical sealing solutions based on real operating conditions.' data-zh='不仅提供产品，更基于实际工况为客户提供优化的密封解决方案。') We go beyond products to deliver practical sealing solutions based on real operating conditions.

        section.about-portfolio
            .about-portfolio-copy
                p.about-section-label(data-i18n='about.portfolio.kicker', data-en='Product Portfolio' data-zh='产品范围') Product Portfolio
                h2.about-section-title.about-portfolio-title
                    span.about-title-zh(data-i18n='about.portfolio.titleZh', data-en='Product Portfolio' data-zh='产品覆盖面广，但这里仅展示概览') Product Portfolio
                    span.about-title-en(data-i18n='about.portfolio.titleEn', data-en='A Broad Portfolio Across Core Sealing Categories' data-zh='A Broad Portfolio Across Core Sealing Categories') A Broad Portfolio Across Core Sealing Categories
                p(data-i18n='about.portfolio.note', data-en='We support both standard supply and customized solutions based on specific application needs.' data-zh='支持标准产品供应及定制化解决方案。') We support both standard supply and customized solutions based on specific application needs.
            .about-portfolio-grid
                span.about-portfolio-tag(data-i18n='about.portfolio.item1', data-en='Hydraulic seals' data-zh='液压密封') Hydraulic seals
                span.about-portfolio-tag(data-i18n='about.portfolio.item2', data-en='Pneumatic seals' data-zh='气动密封') Pneumatic seals
                span.about-portfolio-tag(data-i18n='about.portfolio.item3', data-en='High-pressure seals' data-zh='高压密封') High-pressure seals
                span.about-portfolio-tag(data-i18n='about.portfolio.item4', data-en='O-rings / X-rings' data-zh='O型圈 / 星型圈') O-rings / X-rings
                span.about-portfolio-tag(data-i18n='about.portfolio.item5', data-en='Metal-cased oil seals' data-zh='骨架油封') Metal-cased oil seals
                span.about-portfolio-tag(data-i18n='about.portfolio.item6', data-en='Glyd rings / Step seals' data-zh='格莱圈 / 斯特封') Glyd rings / Step seals
                span.about-portfolio-tag(data-i18n='about.portfolio.item7', data-en='Dust wipers / Water seals' data-zh='防尘 / 水封') Dust wipers / Water seals
                span.about-portfolio-tag(data-i18n='about.portfolio.item8', data-en='Construction machinery seals' data-zh='工程机械密封件') Construction machinery seals

        section.about-value
            .about-value-brand
                p.about-section-label(data-i18n='about.philosophy.kicker', data-en='Why Choose Us' data-zh='经营理念 / 为什么选择我们') Why Choose Us
                h2.about-value-title(data-i18n='about.philosophy.title', data-en='Green · Quality · Service · Integrity' data-zh='绿色 · 品质 · 服务 · 诚信') Green · Quality · Service · Integrity
                p(data-i18n='about.philosophy.copy', data-en='We are committed to delivering reliable products, supporting sustainable development, and building long-term partnerships with our customers.' data-zh='我们致力于在保障产品性能的同时推动可持续发展，并为客户创造长期稳定的合作价值。') We are committed to delivering reliable products, supporting sustainable development, and building long-term partnerships with our customers.
            .about-value-list-wrap
                ul.about-value-list
                    li(data-i18n='about.choose.item1', data-en='Stable quality' data-zh='产品质量稳定可靠') Stable quality
                    li(data-i18n='about.choose.item2', data-en='Wide product availability' data-zh='产品种类齐全') Wide product availability
                    li(data-i18n='about.choose.item3', data-en='Fast response' data-zh='响应快速') Fast response
                    li(data-i18n='about.choose.item4', data-en='Technical support' data-zh='技术支持完善') Technical support
                    li(data-i18n='about.choose.item5', data-en='Flexible solutions' data-zh='可提供灵活解决方案') Flexible solutions
                p.about-value-note(data-i18n='about.choose.copy', data-en='We aim to be your trusted partner in sealing solutions.' data-zh='我们致力于成为您值得信赖的密封系统合作伙伴。') We aim to be your trusted partner in sealing solutions.

        section.about-cta
            .about-cta-inner
                h2.about-cta-title(data-i18n='about.cta.title', data-en='Looking for the Right Sealing Solution?' data-zh='正在寻找合适的密封解决方案？') Looking for the Right Sealing Solution?
                p(data-i18n='about.cta.text', data-en='Contact us for product selection, technical support, or customized solutions.' data-zh='欢迎联系我们，获取产品选型、技术支持或定制化解决方案。') Contact us for product selection, technical support, or customized solutions.
                .about-cta-actions
                    a.btn.btn-primary.btn-xl.text-uppercase(href='contact.html', data-i18n='about.cta.contact', data-en='Contact Us' data-zh='联系我们') Contact Us
                    a.btn.btn-outline-light.btn-xl.text-uppercase(href='products.html', data-i18n='about.cta.products', data-en='View Products' data-zh='查看产品') View Products
